16 Kusalattika, Uppannattika
Kusalattika, Uppannattika
28.
75Kusalo anuppanno dhammo nakusalassa naanuppannassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
76Ārammaṇe aṭṭhārasa, adhipatiyā tīṇi, upanissaye aṭṭhārasa. (Uppādī anuppannasadisaṃ.)
